{"id":38056,"date":"2024-02-22T18:21:49","date_gmt":"2022-09-22T12:51:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=38056"},"modified":"2023-09-30T12:20:16","modified_gmt":"2023-09-30T06:50:16","slug":"book-rack-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/book-rack-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Modern Book Rack Designs: Meet Your Home\u2019s New Conversation Starter"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Stop right here if you\u2019re looking for a book rack design that serves books, looks and conversations!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Books are definitely great conversation starters. But if you\u2019re a bibliophile throwing a house party or inviting friends over, here\u2019s another conversation starter \u2014 your book rack design! Think about it, a book rack is an extension of the reader\u2019s personality. Pick a design that you think best reflects your interest in books. Or you can get a book rack design custom-made for<strong> <\/strong>your home for the kind of relationship you want for yourself or your children with books. So, here are some of our modern book rack design recommendations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mini Book Rack Design For A Leisure Reading Corner<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This compact book rack design is splendid for the occasional reader or those who consider reading a leisure activity to be enjoyed in a relaxing corner such as the balcony. A couch with a storage bench holds just the right amount of books while also saving crucial floor space. As seen in this design, the open cabinets make storage and organisation easy. You may add more character to the reading corner with potted plants, curtains, fairy lights and a rustic side table.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181539\/book-rack-design-occasional-reader.jpg\" alt=\"Book rack design for occasional reader with a storage bench to save floor space\" class=\"wp-image-38058\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181539\/book-rack-design-occasional-reader.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181539\/book-rack-design-occasional-reader-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181539\/book-rack-design-occasional-reader-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181539\/book-rack-design-occasional-reader-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A mini book rack design for the occasional reader<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Freestanding Wooden Book Rack Design With A Twist<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you know a reader who would not trade their prized books or are you them? We mean if you\u2019re the ones who\u2019d use their genius to hide those books in plain sight, this book rack design is apt for<strong> <\/strong>your home. At first glance, the wooden furniture seems to be an ordinary, freestanding wardrobe with cabinets and drawers until you realise it features a folding bookshelf. Yes, the concealed cabinet can be used to secretly stash your books. Apart from privacy for books, this folding bookshelf design is a great use of space and can even be a multipurpose wardrobe. Here\u2019s a smart trick \u2014 use the public cabinet to store fancy china so that no one even imagines the one underneath to contain books.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181616\/wooden-book-rack-design.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden book rack design with a concealed cabinet and folding bookshelf\" class=\"wp-image-38064\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181616\/wooden-book-rack-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181616\/wooden-book-rack-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181616\/wooden-book-rack-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181616\/wooden-book-rack-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A wooden book rack design with a concealed cabinet<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Space-Saving Book Rack Design With TV Unit<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A chic living room look, multifunctional usage, an entertainment unit and accent furniture \u2014 there are many perks in a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/modern-tv-unit-design-ideas\/\">modern TV unit<\/a> as shown here. The floating TV unit, besides saving floor space and making the room appear larger, also makes room for books with independent racks. The space can be divided among family members to feature their collection of books. We also love how the TV section doesn\u2019t overpower the bookshelves, as if to emphasise that books are here to stay. It\u2019s also a great design for reminding young children to stay invested in books.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181610\/space-saving-book-rack-design.jpg\" alt=\"Space-saving book rack design in the tv unit for small living room\" class=\"wp-image-38063\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181610\/space-saving-book-rack-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181610\/space-saving-book-rack-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181610\/space-saving-book-rack-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181610\/space-saving-book-rack-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Space-saving book rack design in the TV unit<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Multipurpose Modern Book Rack Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\u2019re looking for book rack designs for the study room, this design scores full marks for optimal use of space. The corner study features many open shelves to store books and is attached to a long storage bench. The storage bench not only safeguards the books but also provides the reader with a low seating spot to enjoy reading. This is an efficient design for young adults like college students who shuffle books during their study time. The corner seat on the bench and the window seat are refreshing alternatives to sitting on the chair. And if you\u2019re looking for comfortable reading chairs, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/comfortable-reading-table-chair\/\">check out this blog<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181551\/modern-book-rack-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Modern book rack design features open shelves and an attached long storage bench\" class=\"wp-image-38060\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181551\/modern-book-rack-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181551\/modern-book-rack-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181551\/modern-book-rack-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181551\/modern-book-rack-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A low-seating storage for preserving books<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Quirky Book Rack Designs For Children\u2019s Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It\u2019s easy to create playful designs for children\u2019s bedrooms. The trick is in creating something that\u2019s playful yet reinforces life lessons, playfully, of course. Take a look at this bedroom. The large wardrobe has a few open bookshelves such that children can access them conveniently. However, it\u2019s the unusual tree-shaped book rack that sparks curiosity. Over time, such quirky modern book rack designs will encourage young children to understand that books are fertilizers for the mind. For bedtime reading, one of these <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedroom-table-lamps\/\">table lamps<\/a> will be helpful.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181533\/book-rack-design-for-kids-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Book rack design for kids bedroom with open bookshelves\" class=\"wp-image-38057\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181533\/book-rack-design-for-kids-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181533\/book-rack-design-for-kids-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181533\/book-rack-design-for-kids-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181533\/book-rack-design-for-kids-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A quirky book rack design for kids\u2019 bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Modern Wall Book Rack Design For A Study Corner<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A modern wall book rack design<strong> <\/strong>is a haven for voracious readers who need ample space for their books with easy access and simple rack maintenance. The study room provides such readers with a dedicated, open space for reading. In this design, most of the racks are left open for quick reach while some closed cabinets are also provided. Another interesting detail is how the executive study table is attached to a mini book rack, making it multifunctional. The sofa and the window curtains are also useful additions to the space. Want to know more about reading room interiors? Check out our suggestions <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/reading-room-design-ideas\/\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181557\/modern-wall-book-rack-design-for-study-corner.jpg\" alt=\"Modern wall book rack design for study corner with easy access\" class=\"wp-image-38061\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181557\/modern-wall-book-rack-design-for-study-corner.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181557\/modern-wall-book-rack-design-for-study-corner-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181557\/modern-wall-book-rack-design-for-study-corner-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181557\/modern-wall-book-rack-design-for-study-corner-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A wall book rack design is useful for avid readers<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Wall Book Rack Design With Hidden Features<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a simple book rack design that wins our hearts for being discreet. The design seems like a wardrobe until the handle is pulled to reveal the hidden book rack, making guests go wow! And when it\u2019s placed near an open bookshelf as in this design, no one could possibly suspect a treasure trove behind the tall cupboard. Another plus is that the closed two-door cabinets at the bottom of the wide bookshelf ensure optimal storage options. Here are some <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/bookshelf-decor-ideas\/\">decor ideas for your bookshelf<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181603\/modern-wall-book-rack-design-with-hidden-racks.jpg\" alt=\"Modern wall book rack design with hidden book racks\" class=\"wp-image-38062\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181603\/modern-wall-book-rack-design-with-hidden-racks.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181603\/modern-wall-book-rack-design-with-hidden-racks-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181603\/modern-wall-book-rack-design-with-hidden-racks-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/22181603\/modern-wall-book-rack-design-with-hidden-racks-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A modern wall book rack design with tall pull-outs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope bibliophiles find this blog useful for protecting their pile of books and also in expressing themselves through the choicest of modern book rack designs. If you have picked one already or have another design in mind and would like our design experts to bring it to life in your home, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">book an appointment now<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/91.png\"\n                    selected>\n                    +91\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+44\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163955\/44.png\">\n        